data.description: The Landing at Arnold Park is within walking distance of South Park and quaint downtown Fuquay-Varina. This immaculate residence boasts modern amenities including granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and stylish laminate flooring in the living room and entryway and tiled bathrooms. Located just 50 minutes from Fort Liberty and a mere 35 minutes from downtown Raleigh, this property offers the perfect blend of modern living and accessibility.
